101
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:03,420
Yoon Dong Ha.

102
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,230
Čo tam vy dvaja robíte?

103
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:08,370
Rozprávame sa.

104
