keby sme šli tento víkend v prestrojení?

172
00:09:53,090 --> 00:09:54,690
Počúvaj, Yoon Dong Ha.

173
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:56,260
Máš čas tento víkend?

174
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:56,710
Čo?

175
00:09:58,860 --> 00:09:59,740
Vydrž, prosím.

176
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,210
Ahoj. Áno.

177
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,170
Ahoj, mami. Ako sa máš?

178
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:14,120
Čo to robí ten zradca Yoon Dong Ha?

179
00:10:14,610 --> 00:10:16,280
Je možné, že by mohol

180
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,660
predať moje informácie vedúcemu Byunovi?

181
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:22,200
Myslela som, že si v konferenčnej miestnosti.

182
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:24,670
Pozri.

183
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:27,640
Pusti ma, ty zradca.

184
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:29,690
Komu hovoríš zradca?

185
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,470
Tebe! Tebe!

186
00:10:32,990 --> 00:10:34,380
Idem do referenčnej miestnosti.

187
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,320
Roztomilá.

188
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:43,040
Zašepkal mi do ucha: 
"Máš peknú retiazku."

189
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,340
Je veľmi mazaný.

190
00:10:44,340 --> 00:10:45,320
Naozaj?

191
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:51,310 
Určite ti to šteklilo ušné bubienky.
Je mi z toho zlé len pri predstave na to.

192
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:55,150
Baek Na Rae. Prestaň fantazírovať.

193
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:56,380
Prečo nie?

194
